If true, export all Sequences in the exported project.

Type <L=f#C></L><I=C>
Boolean; read/write.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ProjectManager.includeConformedAudio <L=f#D></L><I=D>
 app.projectManager.options.includeConformedAudio 

