Project object <L=g#1></L><I=1>
 app.project 

Description <L=g#2></L><I=2>
Represents a Premiere Pro project. As of Premiere Pro 12.0, multiple projects may be open at the same
time.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Attributes <L=g#3></L><I=3>
