Type <L=g#6></L><I=6>
A Sequence object , or  0  if no sequence is currently active.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Project.cloudProjectlocalID <L=g#7></L><I=7>
 app.project.cloudProjectlocalID 

