String; read-only.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Project.path <L=g#j></L><I=j>
 app.project.path 

Description <L=g#k></L><I=k>
The file path of the project.

Type <L=g#l></L><I=l>
String; read-only.

Example <L=g#m></L><I=m>
Get a path of a curently active project

```javascript
app.project.path; // /Users/USERNAME/Desktop/Project.prproj
```

