Project.createNewSequenceFromClips() <L=g#K></L><I=K>
 app.project.createNewSequenceFromClips(sequenceName, arrayOfProjectItems, [destinationBin]) 

Description <L=g#L></L><I=L>
Creates a new Sequence object with the given name, in the specified destination bin, and sequentially
inserts project items into it.

Parameters <L=g#M></L><I=M>
  Argument                Type                           Description
  ----------------------- ------------------------------ ---------------------------------------------------------
   sequenceName           String                         Optional. A name for a new sequence.
   arrayOfProjectItems    Array of ProjectItem objects   An array of project items to be inserted into sequence.
   destinationBin         ProjectItem object             Optional. A bin to contain sequence.

Returns <L=g#N></L><I=N>
Returns the newly-created Sequence object if successful; 0 if unsuccessful.

