Description <L=m#b></L><I=b>
Add a description

Returns an object, containing similar data

```javascript
{
    value: [
        sRGB,
        BT.601 (NTSC),
        BT.601 (PAL),
        BT.709,
        BT.709 (Scene),
        BT.2020,
        BT.2020 (Scene),
        BT.2100 PQ,
        BT.2100 PQ (Scene),
        BT.2100 HLG,
        BT.2100 HLG (Scene),
        DCDM XYZ,
    ]
};
```

