Type <L=m#f></L><I=f>
String; read/write.

Example <L=m#g></L><I=g>
Rename first project item.

```javascript
var item = app.project.rootItem.children[0];
if (item) {
    item.name = item.name + ', updated by PProPanel.';
} else {
    alert('Could not rename project item');
}
```

