parameters which support keyframing.

Parameters <L=q#q></L><I=q>
  Argument        Type   Description
  --------------- ------ ---------------------------------
   timeToCheck           Start search from a given time.

Returns <L=q#r></L><I=r>
Returns a Time value, indicating when the closest keyframe is, or  0  if there is no available previous
keyframe.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

