|                         |                         |                         | composited at maximum   |
|                         |                         |                         | depth.                  |
+-------------------------+-------------------------+-------------------------+-------------------------+
|  maximumRenderQuality   | Boolean                 |                         | Whether sequence is     |
|                         |                         |                         | rendered at maximum     |
