|                         |                         |     Timecode            |                         |
|                         |                         | -    107  - 59.94       |                         |
|                         |                         |     Non-Drop Timecode   |                         |
|                         |                         | -    108  - 60 Timecode |                         |
|                         |                         | -    109  - Frames      |                         |
|                         |                         | -    110  - 23.976      |                         |
|                         |                         |     Timecode            |                         |
|                         |                         | -    111  - 16mm Feet + |                         |
|                         |                         |     Frames              |                         |
|                         |                         | -    112  - 35mm Feet + |                         |
|                         |                         |     Frames              |                         |
|                         |                         | -    113  - 48 Timecode |                         |
+-------------------------+-------------------------+-------------------------+-------------------------+
