|                         |                         |     by Side             |                         |
+-------------------------+-------------------------+-------------------------+-------------------------+
|  vrProjection           | Integer                 | -    0  - None          | The projection type in  |
|                         |                         | -    1  -               | use, for VR footage.    |
|                         |                         |     Equirectangular     |                         |
+-------------------------+-------------------------+-------------------------+-------------------------+

