Sets the mute state, of the track.

Parameters <L=t#y></L><I=y>
  Argument    Type      Description
  ----------- --------- --------------------------------------------------------------
   isMuted    Integer   If  1  , mute the track. If  0  , the track will be unmuted.

Returns <L=t#z></L><I=z>
Returns  0  if successful.

